(24, 'Are you looking at upgrading your skills and reaching the next level and maximising your full potential. ', 'Meet Nancy, She is the lead Executive Presence, Behavioural Skills Coach & Corporate Storyteller.', '2019-06-18 16:07:22', 'Nancy Katyal', 'nancy-katyal', 'post-bg.jpg', 'personal branding', 'Pune', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Meet Nancy, She is the lead Executive Presence, Behavioural Skills Coach &amp; Corporate Storyteller. She has led key level roles in Education, Insurance and Banking Sector. In 2012, after her corporate stint, she founded The Perfect You. Through her training programs Nancy has been a guide to many esteemed corporate offices, Fortune 500 companies, Luxury brands and SME’s. She is also on board as a mentor at Cherie Blair foundation.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">She was also on the Advisory board panel at TEDxPune and Josh talks. Her views and articles have been featured in the leading national newspapers and magazines like The Times of India, The New Indian Express, Pune mirror, Sakal times and magazines namely Creme, Good housekeeping, Cariz, Perfect Woman , Brand India Magazine etc.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Nancy’s work has grabbed a wealth of praise and media attention. Nancy is a LIMCA Book of record holder for her unique workshop she led along with 11 women.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Nancy is one amongst the 12 Storytellers listed on the International Storytelling network and was featured in the list of Image consultants in India and she is a frequent invitee for key note sessions, inspirational seminars, panel discussions and bespoke sessions for leaders.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">She has coached CEO’s, Celebrities and VP’s of large corporate houses and MNC’s. Nancy is the recipient of several awards including the Lokmat Sakhi Sanman Award for her contribution in Education sector, and the World’s Best Storyteller Award by World HRD Congress bestowed on leading storytellers.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Nancy’s story as an entrepreneur was covered by the leading news channel ZEE (24 taas).</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Executive Presence Coach, Behavioural Skills Advocate&nbsp; &amp; Corporate Storytelling Facilitator:</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Nancy Katyal is considered one of the leading Executive Presence &amp; Storytelling Coaches in corporate circles in India. She has spoken at prestigious forums like CII, Wikipedia, Femina Believe, Toastmasters, Mrs. Maharashtra 2017 &amp; MIT, Pune. She has helped thousands of high powered executives, corporates, celebrities, pageant contestants and people from all walks of life to maximise success in their professional and personal performance. Her clientele includes recognised industry thought leaders, founders&nbsp; of&nbsp; leading&nbsp; start&nbsp; up&nbsp; ventures&nbsp; in&nbsp; the corporate sector as well as leading colleges and management institutes. Each of her session is custom built. Her range of speaking interests include&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Emotional Intelligence, Effective Communication, Personal Branding, Executive Presence, Pillars of Self esteem,&nbsp; &nbsp;Communication Strategies, Public Speaking, Why stories matter and on various management mantras.</span><span style=\"white-space: pre; font-family: Arial;\">	</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Awards:</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Nancy was&nbsp; awarded&nbsp; the&nbsp; Best Trainer &amp; Coach of the Year Award by Lady boss Awards for her outstanding&nbsp; in-dividual achievement in 2018.&nbsp; Subsequently,&nbsp; she&nbsp; was&nbsp; also&nbsp; the&nbsp; recipient&nbsp; of&nbsp; the&nbsp; Lokmat Sakhi Sanman Award, REX Karamveer Chakra Award. She is also the winner of World’s Best Storyteller Award, bestowed on leading storytellers. Nancy’s story was recently featured in a coffee table book called She the change. She is also a LIMCA Book of Record holder. Nancy was also awarded as one amongst the 51 most influential women of the year award&nbsp; by BrijBhumi Foundation and Speaker of the Year Award 2019 by I.N.S.P.I.R.E Beyond Motherhood Awards.&nbsp;</span></p>', 1),
(25, 'Are   you launching a new brand in Pune then meet Priety Mody A pioneer of making guest list for luxury events and making sure they are there for your', 'Preity Mody is the pioneer of curating guest lists for Luxury Events in Pune Priety Mody And has been doing this successfully over 11 years now.', '2019-06-18 16:14:41', 'Preity Modi', 'preity-modi', 'post-bg.jpg', 'personal branding', 'Pune', '<p>Preity Mody is the pioneer Of curating guest lists for Luxury&nbsp; Events in Pune Priety Mody And has been doing this successfully&nbsp; over&nbsp; 11 years Now .</p><p>Her business is inviting luxury and lifestyle potential buyers for luxury / lifestyle launches n events.</p><p>Her work and expertise is connecting luxury buyers with luxury brands since over 11 years now in Pune and Mumbai.</p><p>She successfully done work with brands like Times of India, Audi cars, Mercedes, Shobha asar jewellers of Mumbai, Ranka jewellers&nbsp; Pune. Pand G Jewllers Pune. And many more are her esteemed clients of the City.&nbsp;</p><p>She is the best for creating levents for fashion and home decor ,&nbsp; lounges&nbsp; /Restaurants, beauty and aesthetics&nbsp; and all types of lifestyle brands&nbsp; By her passion she writes a lifestyle blog too&nbsp; and is an Instagram blogger tio .&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>She has won many awards for her outstanding work.</p><p>&nbsp;Times power women in April&nbsp; 2019</p><p>Lokmat visionary award 2017 – 2018</p><p>Punes most powerful award&nbsp; 2018 -2019 by femina</p><p>Been felicitated by INIFD institute as a respected person in field of fashion and&nbsp; luxury and been invited as a judge by then to judge their&nbsp; fashion graduates fashion show</p><p>Preity mody has been felicitated as She’s Mercedez award&nbsp; recognition of being a success full woman by Mercedes&nbsp; Benz</p><p>Along with her events work she has launched her own&nbsp; designer&nbsp; &nbsp;luxury fashion Jewelry brand Eternity in May 2019.</p>', 1);

